---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';


---
<Layout 
title="Privacy Policy | Matt Whitfield"
description= "How I handle your data with respect: privacy policy for Matt Whitfield's web design & development site."
image= "/images/matt-whitfield-bloomsday-2021-400x400.webp"
>
<main class="bg-white min-h-screen py-16">
  <section class="page-container max-w-prose mx-auto neo-card-base p-8 md:p-12 border-3 border-black bg-white shadow-neo mt-16 mb-24">
    <h1 class="neo-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8 text-text">Data Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="neo-text text-lg mb-6">
      I use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use my website—like which pages are helpful and where I can improve. I also have a contact form and an embedded Google Calendar scheduler for appointments. Here’s how I handle your data (spoiler: with respect).
    </p>
    <h2 class="neo-heading text-2xl mt-10 mb-4">What I Collect & Why</h2>
    <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-lg mb-2 mt-6">Google Analytics</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 neo-text mb-4">
      <li>Tracks basic website usage (e.g., page visits, time spent) with anonymized data.</li>
      <li>I’ve disabled personal tracking—your IP address is hidden, and I don’t see who you are.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-lg mb-2 mt-6">Contact Form</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 neo-text mb-4">
      <li>If you email me via the form, I’ll only use your name/email to respond.</li>
      <li>I won’t add you to a mailing list unless you explicitly ask (and you can opt out anytime).</li>
    </ul>
    <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-lg mb-2 mt-6">Google Calendar Scheduler</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 neo-text mb-4">
      <li>When you book an appointment, Google Calendar processes your name, email, and meeting details.</li>
      <li>I only use this to confirm and manage appointments—nothing else.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="neo-heading text-2xl mt-10 mb-4">What I Don’t Do</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 neo-text mb-4">
      <li>I never sell, trade, or misuse your data. Ever.</li>
      <li>I don’t store contact form submissions or calendar bookings outside of Google’s or Netlify's (form data) secure systems.</li>
      <li>I avoid unnecessary data collection (e.g., I won’t ask for your address unless it’s truly needed).</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="neo-heading text-2xl mt-10 mb-4">Your Control</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 neo-text mb-4">
      <li><strong>Opt out of analytics:</strong> Use Google’s opt-out tool or disable cookies in your browser.</li>
      <li><strong>Delete contact history:</strong> Email me to remove past messages.</li>
      <li><strong>Google Calendar data:</strong> Managed via your Google account settings.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="neo-text mt-8 mb-4">I’ll update this policy if anything changes, but your privacy will always come first.</p>
    <p class="neo-text">Questions? Contact me at: <a href="mailto:hello@mattwhitfield.xyz" class="neo-link-base neo-link-primary">hello@mattwhitfield.xyz</a></p>
    <p class="neo-text text-sm text-muted mt-8">Last updated: May, 2025</p>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

